'''威廉·R·埃维尼纳'''（{{lang-en|William R. Evanina}}，{{bd|1967年|||catIdx=McEnany}}）是美国[[国家反情报和安全中心|国家反情报和安全中心]]（NCSC）主任，<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Man Who Protects America's Secrets|url=https://www.npr.org/2017/09/15/551074443/the-man-who-protects-america-s-secrets|accessdate=2020-08-08|work=NPR.org|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020193730/https://www.npr.org/2017/09/15/551074443/the-man-who-protects-america-s-secrets|dead-url=no}}</ref>也是美国政府的国家反情报部门负责人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=NCSC Home|url=https://www.dni.gov/index.php/ncsc-home|accessdate=2020-08-08|work=www.dni.gov|archive-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302105738/https://www.ncsc.gov/nittf/docs/CNSSI-4009_National_Information_Assurance.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>在转入NCSC之前，埃维尼纳曾担任国家反情报执行办公室（ONCIX）的主任。在加入ONCIX之前，他是[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]（CIA）反间谍小组的负责人。[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]（FBI）的工作经历使他获得了最初的执法经验。

== 早年生活与教育 ==
埃维尼纳出生于[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[斯克蘭頓_(賓夕法尼亞州)|斯克兰顿]]的郊区[[佩克维尔|佩克维尔]]，并在那里长大。他的父亲是一位专业音乐人，也是著名的波尔卡乐队“[[宾夕法尼亚风流|宾夕法尼亚风流]]”的创始人。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Graham, Tom|date=30 May 2013|title=Up Close: John Evanina|newspaper=The 570|url=http://the570.com/up-close-john-evanina/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512024209/http://the570.com/up-close-john-evanina/|archivedate=2016-05-12|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=yes}}</ref>埃维尼纳就读于谷景高中，他在那里踢足球和棒球，<ref name="Bolus">{{Cite news|author=Bolus, Kathleen|date=29 June 2014|title=Midvalley resident rises in the ranks of FBI|url=http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/midvalley-resident-rises-in-the-ranks-of-fbi-1.1711108|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702091450/http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/midvalley-resident-rises-in-the-ranks-of-fbi-1.1711108|archivedate=2015-07-02|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>In his senior year of high school, Evanina made the Lackawanna League Northern Division baseball all-star team {{Cite news|author=Myers, Marty|date=20 June 2015|title=30, 20 and 10 years ago: A look back at sports headlines|newspaper=The Scranton Times-Tribune|url=http://m.thetimes-tribune.com/sports/30-20-and-10-years-ago-a-look-back-at-sports-headlines-1.1901083|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRW8EH4n?url=http://m.thetimes-tribune.com/sports/30-20-and-10-years-ago-a-look-back-at-sports-headlines-1.1901083|archivedate=2016-05-12|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后在[[基斯通学院|基斯通学院]]（Keystone College）继续打棒球。<ref name="Bolus" /> 然后，他转到附近的[[威尔克斯大学|威尔克斯大学]]（Wilkes University），并于1989年以[[拉丁文學位榮譽|优异]]的成绩获得了公共管理学士学位。<ref name="Mayk">{{Cite web|title=National Counterintelligence Executive William Evanina Delivers Economic Espionage Lecture Nov. 12 At Wilkes University|url=http://www.wilkes.edu/news/2015/October/william-evanina-economic-espionage.aspx|accessdate=|author=Mayk, Vicki|date=23 October 2015|format=|publisher=Wilkes University|language=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRKxNG0I?url=http://www.wilkes.edu/news/2015/October/william-evanina-economic-espionage.aspx|archivedate=2016-05-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>在联邦调查局任职期间，他于2008年在[[阿卡迪亚大学|阿卡迪亚大学]]（Arcadia University）获得了教育领导学硕士学位。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Allabaugh, Denise|date=3 November 2015|title=National intelligence exec, NEPA native, to discuss cybersecurity|newspaper=The Scranton Times-Tribune|url=http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/business/national-intelligence-exec-nepa-native-to-discuss-cybersecurity-1.1966242|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512014405/http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/business/national-intelligence-exec-nepa-native-to-discuss-cybersecurity-1.1966242|archivedate=2016-05-12|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 职业生涯 ==
大学毕业后，埃维尼纳到总务管理局工作，在那里他是新建筑部门的项目经理。<ref name="Bolus-2">{{Cite news|author=Bolus, Kathleen|date=30 June 2014|title=FBI agent credits NEPA values for work ethic|newspaper=The Citizens' Voice|location=Wilkes-Barre, Pennsylvania|url=http://citizensvoice.com/news/fbi-agent-credits-nepa-values-for-work-ethic-1.1711183|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRMcNrsY?url=http://citizensvoice.com/news/fbi-agent-credits-nepa-values-for-work-ethic-1.1711183|archivedate=2016-05-12|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>1996年，他加入了联邦调查局成为特工，并在暴力犯罪部门，有组织犯罪部门以及银行抢劫和反恐怖主义部门工作过。他后来还曾在联邦调查局的国家安全处和反情报部门工作。他成为一名经过认证的特警队成员以及一名经过认证的狙击手。在此期间，他参与了对2001年9月11日[[聯合航空93號班機恐怖襲擊|联合航空93号航班]]劫机事件，[[2001年美國炭疽攻擊事件|2001年美国炭疽攻击事件]]和[[丹尼尔·珀尔|丹尼尔·珀尔]]（Daniel Pearl）绑架案的调查。<ref name="SINET">{{Cite web|title=Bill Evanina|url=http://www.security-innovation.org/bios/Bill_Evanina.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=SINET (Security Innovation Network)|language=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRJtXJuQ?url=http://www.security-innovation.org/bios/Bill_Evanina.htm|archivedate=2016-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2004年6月，他被任命为新設立的联合恐怖主义特别工作组的监督特工。随后发生了一起海关泄密事件，他领导了对位于新泽西州蒙茅斯堡的FBI情报分析师活动的调查，该情报分析师向[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]各方泄漏机密信息。埃维尼纳的工作使[[莱安德罗·阿拉贡基洛|莱安德罗·阿拉贡基洛]]（Leandro Aragoncillo）因从事间谍活动而被定罪，埃维尼纳因此荣获FBI杰出指挥奖。2006年1月，他被任命为联邦调查局在特伦顿市新泽西办事处的高级督导常驻代理（SSRA）。2009年3月，他被分配到华盛顿办公室，并在联邦调查局的国家安全部门工作，在那里他领导了反情报和反恐行动。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Associated Press|date=17 January 2006|title=FBI Missed Signs of Espionage in Filipino Case|newspaper=Fox News|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/01/17/fbi-missed-signs-espionage-in-filipino-case.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512032551/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/01/17/fbi-missed-signs-espionage-in-filipino-case.html|archivedate=2016-05-12|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年9月，埃维尼纳被任命为联邦调查局和中央情报局反情报部门/反间谍小组的联合负责人，在那里他协调了来自多个情报机构的人员，以打击外国间谍活动。 2014年6月，2014年6月，他被[[詹姆斯·R·克拉珀|詹姆斯·R·克拉珀]]（James R. Clapper）任命为国家反情报执行办公室的主任，接替了弗兰克·蒙托亚（Frank Montoya）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=DNI Appoints New National Counterintelligence Executive|url=https://www.dni.gov/index.php/newsroom/press-releases/198-press-releases-2014/1073-dni-appoints-new-national-counterintelligence-executive|accessdate=|author=|date=12 June 2014|format=|publisher=Office of the Director of National Intelligence|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512041140/https://www.dni.gov/index.php/newsroom/press-releases/198-press-releases-2014/1073-dni-appoints-new-national-counterintelligence-executive|archivedate=2016-05-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Knauth">{{Cite magazine|last=Knauth|first=Dietrich|date=13 February 2018|title=Trump Nominates Evanina To Stay On As Counterintel Head|url=https://www.washingtonexec.com/2018/02/trump-nominates-evanina-director-counterintelligence/|magazine=WashingtonExec|page=|doi=|pmid=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503193453/https://www.washingtonexec.com/2018/02/trump-nominates-evanina-director-counterintelligence/|archive-date=2018-05-03|access-date=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=U.S. counter-spy chief cuffs driver who rammed restaurant|date=6 May 2016|newspaper=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-security-fire-idUSKCN0XW2DX|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRPQ68ig?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-security-fire-idUSKCN0XW2DX|archivedate=2016-05-12|author=|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Meet the Man Who's Gauging the Damage From Snowden|url=http://www.govexec.com/management/2014/08/meet-man-whos-gauging-damage-snowden/91595/|accessdate=|author=|date=15 August 2014|last=Clark|first=Charles S.|format=|publisher=Government Executive (National Journal Group, Inc.)|language=|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6hRRrOdds?url=http://www.govexec.com/management/2014/08/meet-man-whos-gauging-damage-snowden/91595/|archivedate=2016-05-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2017年5月解雇[[詹姆斯·科米|詹姆斯·科米]]（James Comey）之后，埃维尼纳曾被考虑担任联邦调查局的临时主管；<ref>{{Cite news|last=Cameron|first=Peter|date=12 May 2017|title=Blakely native in running to be interim director of FBI|newspaper=[[The_Scranton_Times-Tribune|The Scranton Times-Tribune]]|url=http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/blakely-native-in-running-to-be-interim-director-of-fbi-1.2191977|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6vpXB4AoL?url=http://thetimes-tribune.com/news/blakely-native-in-running-to-be-interim-director-of-fbi-1.2191977|archive-date=2017-12-19|author=|work=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而[[安德魯·麥卡比|安德鲁·麦凯布]]（Andrew G. McCabe）继续担任FBI代理局长，直到2017年8月任命[[克里斯托弗·A·雷|克里斯托弗·A·雷]]（Christopher A. Wray）。<ref>{{Cite magazine |last=Kutner |first=Max |date=2 Aug 2017 |title=Under New Bureau Head, Acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe to Remain as Deputy, Despite Trump’s Allegations |magazine=Newsweek |url=http://www.newsweek.com/christopher-wray-fbi-director-andrew-mccabe-deputy-645600 |access-date=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223225153/https://www.newsweek.com/christopher-wray-fbi-director-andrew-mccabe-deputy-645600 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2018年2月，[[唐納·川普|特朗普总统]]正式提名埃维尼纳为美国国家反情报和安全中心主任。<ref>The Senate Select Committee for Intelligence held his nomination hearings on 15 May 2018, and an approval recommendation was sent to the Senate on 22 May. {{Cite web|title=PN1548 — William R. Evanina — Office of the Director of National Intelligence|url=https://www.congress.gov/nomination/115th-congress/1548|publisher=United States Senate|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2018-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206091641/https://www.congress.gov/nomination/115th-congress/1548|dead-url=no}}; {{Cite web|title=Senate Intel Unanimously Approves Evanina to Continue as NCSC Director, Nomination Moves to Full Senate|url=https://www.burr.senate.gov/press/releases/senate-intel-unanimously-approves-evanina-to-continue-as-ncsc-director-nomination-moves-to-full-senate|accessdate=|author=|date=22 May 2018|format=|publisher=United States Senator Richard Burr|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726181744/https://www.burr.senate.gov/press/releases/senate-intel-unanimously-approves-evanina-to-continue-as-ncsc-director-nomination-moves-to-full-senate|archive-date=2018-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2020年5月6日，美国参议院以84票对7票投票批准了他的提名。

